{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":11,"day":8}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"华主席身穿绿军装","authors":["余光烈"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动的心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快要蹦出胸膛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的泪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已涌满眼眶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过沸腾的旗海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过起伏的花浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见了，看见了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席站在天安门城楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿一身绿色军装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚激情呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象奔腾的黄河；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔思绪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如汹涌的大江……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士呵，怎能忘记——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年前幸福的时光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门上红日升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席身穿绿军装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着绿军装呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱想起韶山的翠竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山的苍松；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着红五星呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱想起长征路上的篝火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延安枣园的灯光……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呵毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫漫革命征途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您亲手为我们导航。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿枪林，跨火海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱迷雾，斗恶浪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"险山恶水化坦途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下捷报千万张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命步步攀高峰呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一声春雷响！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天呵，华主席身穿绿军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍然屹立在天安门上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士滔滔的思绪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作惊雷震长天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士滚滚的激情呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象大江又掀千尺浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年前的喜泪接着淌呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年前的颂歌接着唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席呵华主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您为首的党中央"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠实继承毛主席遗志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横扫乌云，力挽狂澜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彻底粉碎了“四人帮”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您为首的党中央"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢捍卫毛主席革命路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶着狂风，踩着惊涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽救了革命挽救了党！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席呵华主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您是全党当之无愧的英明领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"率领全党、全军、全国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又写出继续革命新篇章！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼望天安门呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注目绿军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满怀豪情按不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千股暖流涌心房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席事业后继有人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的洪流不可阻挡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的党呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有了英明的领袖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的航船呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有了舵手把舵掌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的华主席呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士一定跟着您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕它万道险阻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕它千重风浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着毛主席的革命路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路高歌向前方！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}